author: Russell Brand
description:
Trump threatens to fine California as trans athletes dominate girls' state championships. In this fiery episode of Actual Friends, Russell, Dave Rubin, and Sage Steele break down the collapse of fairness in women’s sports—and the cultural rot behind it. Are we watching the end of truth itself? From Gavin Newsom’s double-speak to fathers staying silent while their daughters are sidelined, the conversation pulls no punches.
